{"tid":2277063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡錫進：美國將進入極不尋常的過渡期","createTime":"2020-11-08T08:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T16:41:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b189dda7888c34a84c08040937b3385e3cd8dccf","tid":2277063,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"內地環球時報總編輯胡錫進認為，美國將進入極不尋常的過渡期，中國需要與拜登團隊發展聯繫，同時不要剌激特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進在社交網站貼文，認為這個將會是美國最為動盪、不確定因素最多的過渡期，中國一定要有底綫思維，做好應變準備，要與拜登團隊發展聯繫，探尋中美關係擺脫極端動盪的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進說，由於特朗普不接受選舉結果，他將這一切向美國外部發洩，比對內發洩更加容易，中方應有意識，避免把特朗普敗選怨氣引向中美關係方向，尤其對特朗普本人保持應有尊重，中國人無必要踩他、挖苦他。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558941-20201108.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558941-20201108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq78orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=a9fa1f28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558941-20201108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bdd127d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558941-20201108.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e8ab3b07681ea58f433c64bd4dff80522e930731","tid":2277063,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"佢咁講即係有機會翻盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368fe98ebb8e2221b31939218d4ec70606c3e57b","tid":2277063,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/2878/1*VQKfFRo-ixoUSE77MJutmw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F2878%2F1%2AVQKfFRo-ixoUSE77MJutmw.png&h=961b47ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2016/12/13/phpgAexoU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%